* Editor's note: Earlier we incorrectly mentioned that Unathi Msgengana was getting a divorce. She did in fact confirm that she and her husband are separated. JOHANNESBURG – Former Metro FM DJ and Idols judge Unathi Msengana has for the first time confirmed she is separated from her long-term husband, Thomas ‘Bad Boy T’ Msengana. Rumours have been doing the rounds for several months that the couple’s marriage is on the rocks. Unathi confirmed the separation on Saturday morning during an interview with the Weekend Wake Up's Ayanda-Allie Paine. “We are in a good place, we’re family,” she said. The pair, who have been married since 2009, have children together. eNCA